{"tid":2397024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獲京贈兩萬支疫苗  一日轉軚 圭亞那撤台辦事處","createTime":"2021-02-06T05:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T06:25:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"79e3e65b736e080c3d2be7e8a3886f934f462034","tid":2397024,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T05:46:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210206/D7LCTAZLYNCOFDYJ4HT55OEAPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210206%2FD7LCTAZLYNCOFDYJ4HT55OEAPU%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIZzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=d267721a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210206%2FD7LCTAZLYNCOFDYJ4HT55OEAPU%2F&h=065c7fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210206/D7LCTAZLYNCOFDYJ4HT55OEAPU/</a><br />\n<br />\n獲京贈兩萬支疫苗 <br />\n一日轉軚 圭亞那撤台辦事處<br />\n<br />\n台灣前天宣佈在南美國家圭亞那設「台灣辦事處」後，北京立即向圭國施「疫苗外交」，贈送兩萬支國產疫苗後，圭國在24小時內隨即「掉轉槍頭」，發聲明稱與台簽署的協議屬「誤解（miscommunication）」，協議終止，強調承認「一個中國」。對此，台灣總統蔡英文發炮，轟習近平上月才稱「反對恃強凌弱，不能誰胳膊粗、拳頭大誰說了算」，今次北京的做法是莫大諷刺。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：贈飛機賄高官 陸銀彈搶台邦交<br />\n<br />\n前天早上，台外交部突然宣佈已在1月中在圭亞那設「台灣辦公室」（Taiwan Office），並已開始初步運作，外界形容「辦公室」實則上是「大使館」，被指是習近平上任後，台罕有地成功撬動北京的外交國，且還以「台灣」名義設處。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/petIuqJ8JQwtJysfuXVeap2U-js=/1886x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F6XXVCU245GLHBCOXLEBW3PWJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpetIuqJ8JQwtJysfuXVeap2U-js%3D%2F1886x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF6XXVCU245GLHBCOXLEBW3PWJA.jpg&h=21aa6220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■圭國外長托德（右）上載與中國駐當地代表陳錫來的合照。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文轟習近平「恃強凌弱」<br />\n<br />\n有涉外人士向台灣蘋果新聞網稱，當時消息一出，北京內部譁然，無法接受。由於大陸駐圭亞那大使上月剛離任，北京隨即改派駐當地的代辦於當地時間與圭國外交部見面，據悉北京曾威脅停止金錢及武漢肺炎疫苗援助圭國。<br />\n<br />\n中圭雙方會談完結後，圭國外交。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文對圭亞那在北京打壓下單方面終止。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拜登撐台 美聞訊感震驚<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人汪文斌直斥：「台灣的分裂行徑和拙劣表演不得人心，注定貽笑大方。」他讚揚圭方及時糾正錯誤，有利於雙邊關係大局。台灣涉外人士指出，美國總統拜登相當支持台於圭國設台灣辦事處，美駐該國大使館得悉圭亞拿轉軚，相當震驚。<br />\n<br />\n根據當地媒體報道，圭亞那在當地時間4日新增66宗武漢肺炎，總。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果新聞網》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/78hPJC9yw02SMvBQRAZqV-qGY4Q=/619x1043/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LXMYPLTKHBBEDCXSNHITTCHBA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F78hPJC9yw02SMvBQRAZqV-qGY4Q%3D%2F619x1043%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLXMYPLTKHBBEDCXSNHITTCHBA4.jpg&h=bb338079&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eef2ff9f6ea5501ae8003ad02791d911ae529d7c","tid":2397024,"uid":20473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T05:47:43.000Z","msg":"好快好多小國有樣學樣同台灣簽約R着數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be30bd476a9df08274ab22c70cc2e28713ba12da","tid":2397024,"uid":282362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"国產疫苗都有人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f9bdae4e7a856af95f2aaf4b9b995eb16ad0e6","tid":2397024,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T05:48:46.000Z","msg":"中國為咗攞威比人當水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8037ee40ef90c207033724ba464d01900ce28fd6","tid":2397024,"uid":388108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eef2ff9f6ea5501ae8003ad02791d911ae529d7c","tid":2397024,"uid":20473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T05:47:43.000Z","msg":"好快好多小國有樣學樣同台灣簽約R着數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T05:4